            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Court Week</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The January term of Court has brought a great many people to our town.
                    Several interesting trials are to come off, and as usual the niggers are well
                    represented and several days and some hundreds of dollars of the people's money
                    will be spent in this most rediculous farce of the law. We think, if it could be
                    done, a seperate Court, in which the darkies, iwth the Lawyers and Migistrates
                    could get justice, should be established and until this is done, let the people
                    recollect that at MILLER's Drug Store, on the Diamond, is the place to buy the
                    best and cheapest of medicines."</excerpt>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Racist screed attacking blacks's participation in the legal system. Defines
                    "the people" in terms of race. Also includes an open solicitation for commercial
                    business at a local merchant.</summary>
                <note/>
            </div>
